00:00:04.800 --> 00:00:07.500
We're gonna talk about
training range of motion today.

00:00:10.250 --> 00:00:12.900
Give it a couple of minutes
for everybody to show up.

00:00:13.920 --> 00:00:16.190
Did everybody see my new X3 cup?

00:00:16.190 --> 00:00:17.700
